abstract: >
  This repository provides the unified manuscript, code, processed data products,
  and results for Structured Orb Dynamics, a geometry-based framework for
  analyzing motion in infrared aerial datasets lacking physical calibration
  metadata. The approach relies exclusively on image-plane measurementsâ€”
  trajectory extraction, curvature diagnostics, and a small discrete motion-state
  classifier. PR-018 is used as an example dataset to illustrate how geometric
  inference can be performed without assumptions about range, propulsion, or
  physical mechanism.

